          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-1" n="1">Peruse my leaves through every part,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-2" n="2">And think thou see'st my owner's heart,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-3" n="3">Scrawl'd o'er with trifles thus, and quite</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-4" n="4">As hard, as senseless, and as light;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-5" n="5">Expos'd to every coxcomb's eyes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-6" n="6">But hid with caution from the wise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-7" n="7">Here you may read── <hi rend="italics">dear charming saint</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-8" n="8">Beneath── <hi rend="italics">a true receipt for paint</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-9" n="9">Here, in beau spelling── <hi rend="italics">tru tel deth</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-10" n="10">There, in her own── <hi rend="italics">far an el breth</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-11" n="11">Here── <hi rend="italics">lovely nymph, pronounce my doom</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-12" n="12">There── <hi rend="italics">a safe way to use perfume</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-13" n="13">Here a page fill'd with billet-doux;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-14" n="14">On t'other side── <hi rend="italics">laid out for shoes</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-15" n="15">Madam, I die without your grace;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-16" n="16">Item── <hi rend="italics">for half a yard of lace</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-17" n="17">Who that had wit would place it here</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-18" n="18">For ev'ry peeping fop to jeer?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-19" n="19">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-20" n="20">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-21" n="21">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-22" n="22">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-23" n="23">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-24" n="24">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-25" n="25">Whoe'er expects to hold his part</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-26" n="26">In such a book and such a heart,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-27" n="27">If he be wealthy and a fool,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-28" n="28">Is in all points the fittest tool;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-29" n="29">Of whom it may be justly said,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-060-04B1-line-30" n="30">He's a gold pencil tipp'd with lead.</l>
          </lg>
